               <p>Passing through the narrow passage that leads from <placeName id="t17840225-47-crimeloc255">Cock-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17840225-47-crimeloc255" type="placeName" value="Cock-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17840225-47-crimeloc255" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840225-47-off253 t17840225-47-crimeloc255"></join> to <placeName id="t17840225-47-crimeloc256">Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17840225-47-crimeloc256" type="placeName" value="Smithfield"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17840225-47-crimeloc256" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840225-47-off253 t17840225-47-crimeloc256"></join>, I heard<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178402250123"></xptr> a person in great haste behind me; I had a child, and made way for him; I felt in my pocket, and my handkerchief was gone, I stepped hastily after him, he looked at me, I followed him, he turned down Hosier-lane, I said I am after you, then he began to run, I ran after him and overtook him, I immediately saw him drop that handkerchief at his left foot.</p>
               <p>(The handkerchief deposed to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840225-47-person584">
                  RICHARD
                   COTTRELL
