                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>The prosecutor brought the prisoner up himself to my door, and gave charge of him, and gave me the handkerchief, and I have had it ever since.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have nothing to say, I have no witnesses.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840225-47-verdict257" type="verdictDescription">
