            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Court. Where do you belong to? - St. Bride's, Fleet-street.</p>
               <p>Have you any father or mother? - No.</p>
               <p>How have you got your living? - I have worked at <rs id="t17840225-47-deflabel260" type="occupation">portering</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840225-47-defend580 t17840225-47-deflabel260"></join> with Mr. Hemings, a fruiterer.</p>
               <p>How comes it he is not here to give you a character? - I would not wish to trouble him.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
